The 22-ft. Fast Charge Electric Trolley has a driving range is approximately 45 miles between charges, which can be completed in about 30 minutes with the Ebus-built 90-kW Fast-Charger. Battery system is single string of 50 100AH SAFT nickel-cadmium liquid-cooled modules.
